PEM-seq comprehensively quantifies DNA repair outcomes during gene-editing and 
DSB repair.

Liu Y(1), Yin J(1), Gan T(1), Liu M(1), Xin C(1), Zhang W(1), Hu J(1).

Author information:
(1)The MOE Key Laboratory of Cell Proliferation and Differentiation, School of 
Life Sciences, Center for Life Sciences, Genome Editing Research Center, Peking 
